---

<div
    class="DrIntro min-h-screen w-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-5 p-4 md:p-8 overflow-x-hidden"
>
    <div class="w-full max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="heading-container mb-6 md:mb-10">
            <h1
                class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight"
            >
                Behind Every Great Smile
                <br class="md:block hidden" />
                <span class="block md:inline">is a Great Doctor</span>
            </h1>
            <div class="w-24 md:w-36 h-1 md:h-[2px] mt-3 md:mt-4 bg-black">
            </div>
        </div>

        <div
            class="relative w-full flex flex-col md:flex-row rounded-lg bg-pink-50 shadow-md overflow-hidden"
        >
            <div
                class="p-4 md:p-6 lg:p-8 w-full md:w-[65%] lg:w-[70%] flex flex-col gap-2 md:gap-3 z-10"
            >
                <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold">
                    Dr. Yukti Ghei Gupta
                </h2>
                <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-800">B.D.S, M.D.S</h3>
                <p
                    class="font-light text-gray-700 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed"
                >
                    Dr. Yukti Ghei Gupta (B.D.S, M.D.S) is a skilled and caring
                    dental specialist known for her gentle approach and expert
                    treatments. With years of experience and a passion for smile
                    makeovers, she helps patients feel confident and
                    comfortable. Whether it's routine care or advanced dental
                    work, Dr. Yukti is trusted for delivering quality results
                    with a personal touch.
                </p>
                <button
                    onclick="document.getElementById('contactUs').scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth' })"
                    class="mt-4 px-3 py-2 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-500 to-purple-600 text-white font-semibold text-sm md:text-md shadow-lg transform transition duration-300 ease-in-out hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-xl focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-400 focus:ring-opacity-50 w-fit cursor-pointer"
                >
                    Book Appointment
                </button>
            </div>
            <div
                class="DrImg w-full md:w-auto flex justify-center md:justify-end"
            >
                <img
                    class="w-48 md:w-auto max-w-full md:max-w-[35%] lg:max-w-[30%] h-auto md:h-full object-contain md:object-cover md:absolute bottom-0 right-0"
                    src="/face.png"
                    alt="Dr. Yukti Ghei Gupta"
                    loading="eager"
                />
            </div>
        </div>

        <div
            class="credentials mt-6 md:mt-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 md:gap-8"
        >
            <div
                class="credential-card p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm flex flex-col items-center"
            >
                <span class="text-3xl text-[#7154FF] font-bold">10+</span>
                <span class="text-gray-700">Years Experience</span>
            </div>
            <div
                class="credential-card p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm flex flex-col items-center"
            >
                <span class="text-3xl text-[#7154FF] font-bold">5000+</span>
                <span class="text-gray-700">Happy Patients</span>
            </div>
            <div
                class="credential-card p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm flex flex-col items-center"
            >
                <span class="text-3xl text-[#7154FF] font-bold">100%</span>
                <span class="text-gray-700">Satisfaction</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .DrImg img {
            position: relative;
            margin-top: -20px;
        }
    }
</style>
